11.1 Pregnancy and maternity leave benefits  

An employee who is pregnant or gives birth is entitled to the following benefits:  

• Five days off to attend five pregnancy examinations;  
• In case of miscarriage, 10 days off work for a pregnancy of less than one month, 20 days 
for a pregnancy of one month to less than three months, 40 days for a pregnancy of three 
months to less than six months, and 50 days for a pregnancy of six months or more;

